    <p class="lede" style="margin:0 0 28px;max-width:72ch;">Training is not a fixed package with a sticker price, because needs vary enormously &mdash; one person learning bank feeds is a different engagement from a five-person team learning the full monthly routine. We don&rsquo;t publish a per-hour or per-session rate we can&rsquo;t stand behind for your situation. Here is exactly how pricing works.</p>
