    <h2 class="h2" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Certified across the full product line. Independent. No commission.</h2>
    <div class="prose">
      <p>QuickBooks training is only as good as the depth of platform knowledge behind it. Every TechBrot training engagement is delivered by a ProAdvisor holding active certifications across QuickBooks Online (Level 2), Desktop, Enterprise, and Payroll &mdash; so the instruction is accurate whether your team is on QBO, Desktop, or Enterprise, and whether the session covers bank feeds, reconciliation, reporting, or a payroll run. Intuit issues those certifications; our team holds them. We are an independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc., not an Intuit-authorized training partner, and not the issuer of the ProAdvisor credential.</p>
      <p>We earn nothing from your QuickBooks subscription &mdash; no Intuit affiliate revenue, no commissions &mdash; so the training reflects how to use the product you have well, not how to upsell you onto a more expensive plan. You can <a href="/quickbooks/proadvisor-team/">meet the ProAdvisor team</a> or read our <a href="/trust/">trust &amp; methodology standards</a>. Independent firm &mdash; not affiliated with Intuit Inc.</p>
